  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The film has to be done excited from-- from the people-- from the way Schindler was sitting on a horse over there, somewhere.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One of the true is when they were being expelled, and they expelled someone else.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] was very hot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was true that he asked one soldier to put the water over the-- besides that one, [? whether things ?] are true, I couldn't tell you.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But, generally, I accepted that the film, that this expressed what-- what most of the people have been going through.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I am very happy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because of-- that's why I read to you, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This-- one thing that you have to do, you have to be happy that somebody who was, when other people have the same opportunity to take the chances.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They have been very honest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even to this point that they have been taking some valuables from people who were working for them, and when they will be alive after the war, they will give them back, and they give them back.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they will not take the chance, to take the risk, to save them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Schindler has agreement with one of them that he take part of his foremans to-- to his factory to-- to Brinnitz.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But Schindler proposed [? him ?] to-- to do the same factory in Brinnlitz, he doesn't want it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm finished, I believe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have nothing else to say.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
